strategy_response: I went about this task by choosing which category was more important to me as a consumer and which I was willing to sacrifice. For example, I was willing to have a lower cooking power for the best warranty since I could always get a new one if I found the cooking power was not suitable for me. Additionally, lifespan was super important to me for expensive appliances- but only if the other category had a suffiecient score.
